title: Waterfront (1944 film noir)
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0037446/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0037446/</a>

This is NOT On The Waterfront with Marlon Brando.

Waterfront is a very low budget espio-noir that I have enjoyed watching more than most of it's kind. See also Steve Sekely's The Scar, which I will also be uploading. It is a much better movie by all accounts, but Waterfront isn't too bad.
